
############# Gmail account
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User skyekingfreeman@gmail.com
PassCmd "security find-generic-password -a gmail -w"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/cert.pem
AuthMechs PLAIN

# Remote Storage
IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

# Local storage
MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox

# Channels
Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *


